Package: qpcrpipeline
Title: MIQE-aligned qPCR Data Cleaning and Consolidation Pipeline
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: person("Jack", "Pepper", email = "jack.pepper@thekids.org.au", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R package for cleaning, auditing, and consolidating quantitative PCR (qPCR) data exported from CFX Maestro. Implements MIQE-aligned quality control checks, LOD classification, and target consolidation into structured Excel workbooks. Fully supports piped workflows.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
